# ML artifacts.
# NOTE: trained models (*.pkl) and the raw data snapshot ARE committed on purpose —
# the live Streamlit app loads them at runtime. Only regenerable artifacts are ignored.
# (processed feature table is regenerable by scripts/build_features.py)
ml/data/processed/
ml/models/*.joblib

